---
// HeroSection.astro
---

<section id="hero" class="hero-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-header">
      <h1 class="hero-title">SOFÍA</h1>
      <h2 class="hero-subtitle">ARTISTA & DISEÑADORA</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-image-wrapper">
        <div class="blob-shape">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?q=80&w=1887&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Portrait" class="hero-img" />
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="hero-text-content">
        <p>
          Creando experiencias visuales que trascienden lo ordinario. 
          Mi trabajo reside en la intersección entre la expresión artística pura 
          y la funcionalidad del diseño moderno.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: var(--color-sand-100, #ECDFCC); /* Fallback to beige */
    color: var(--color-steel-200, #687A92);
  }

  .container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  /* Header Styles */
  .hero-header {
    text-align: center;
    animation: fadeInDown 1s ease-out;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 15vw, 12rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    color: var(--color-sand-300, #C1AD94);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--color-steel-100, #8597A5);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  /* Grid Layout */
  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: end; /* Align items to the bottom as requested */
  }

  /* Image Blob */
  .hero-image-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    animation: fadeInLeft 1s ease-out 0.3s backwards;
  }

  .blob-shape {
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    border-radius: 60% 40% 30% 70% / 60% 30% 70% 40%;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 20px 20px 0px var(--color-sand-200, #E3CAAB);
    animation: morph 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .hero-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transform: scale(1.1); /* Slight zoom for parallax feel effect */
  }

  /* Text Content */
  .hero-text-content {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    animation: fadeInRight 1s ease-out 0.6s backwards;
  }

  .hero-text-content p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 400px;
    text-align: right; /* Align text to right as implied by placement */
    color: var(--color-steel-200, #687A92);
  }

  /* Animations */
  @keyframes morph {
    0% { border-radius: 60% 40% 30% 70% / 60% 30% 70% 40%; }
    50% { border-radius: 30% 60% 70% 40% / 50% 60% 30% 60%; }
    100% { border-radius: 60% 40% 30% 70% / 60% 30% 70% 40%; }
  }

  @keyframes fadeInDown {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes fadeInLeft {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
  }

  @keyframes fadeInRight {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-image-wrapper {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-text-content {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-text-content p {
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .blob-shape {
        width: 300px;
        height: 300px;
    }
  }
</style>
